Write a C program to scan the string from the user and to print it

INPUT  & OUTPUT FORMAT: 

Input consists of 1 string.

Output consists of 1 string.

Sample Input:
Cyfuno

Sample Output:

The string is Cyfuno

//coding

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    string str;
    cin>>str;
    cout<<"The string is "<<str;
}
